						<div class="postbody">So the only difference between your coding style and my coding style is that you're not doing sound in VBlank routine, and that you're still doing random number generation/joypad reading or something between VBlank pass check, but I personally rather prefer do only VBlank check, and my random number generation routine is called once at the end of my VBlank routine (actually those are the only two non-PPU stuff I do in my VBlank routine, sound and random number, along with setting VBlank flags).</div>

					
